WEBVTT

00:01.302 --> 00:02.534
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON</i>
<i> "IF LOVING YOU IS WRONG"...</i>

00:02.570 --> 00:05.137
THE MEETING IS TOMORROW
WITH THE BOARD AT THE HOSPITAL,

00:05.172 --> 00:06.638
SO YOU CAN TELL THEM
THE TRUTH.

00:06.674 --> 00:08.841
YES, YES, I-I -- YES.
I WILL BE THERE.

00:08.876 --> 00:10.075
I'M ATTORNEY CARL ADAMS.

00:10.111 --> 00:11.276
-PUBLIC DEFENDER'S OFFICE?
-YEAH.

00:11.312 --> 00:13.812
PROSECUTOR OFFERED YOU A DEAL.
LIFE FOR BOTH CRIMES.

00:13.848 --> 00:15.080
I THINK YOU'RE FIRED.

00:15.116 --> 00:16.849
-IAN, THIS IS -- THIS --
-JENNIFER. YEAH, WE'VE MET.

00:16.884 --> 00:18.851
NO, I'M -- I'M ALEX.

00:18.886 --> 00:20.519
I'M SORRY. I THOUGHT
YOU WERE SOMEONE ELSE.

00:20.554 --> 00:23.422
SHE WANTED TO KNOW IF YOU COULD
LOOK OVER HER DIVORCE PAPERS.

00:23.457 --> 00:24.623
THEY'RE AT MY HOUSE.

00:24.658 --> 00:25.624
SO I'LL JUST --
I'LL RUN BACK AND GET THEM.

00:25.659 --> 00:27.359
-OKAY, I'LL WALK YOU OVER.
-OKAY.

00:29.864 --> 00:31.430
WH-WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

00:31.465 --> 00:32.364
GET OFF OF ME.

00:32.400 --> 00:34.333
OH, COME ON.

00:34.368 --> 00:36.301
"OH, COME ON"?

00:36.337 --> 00:38.036
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE.

00:38.072 --> 00:39.071
O-OKAY.

00:39.106 --> 00:40.706
I THOUGHT THAT'S
WHAT YOU WANTED.

00:40.741 --> 00:42.374
YOU'RE WRONG.

00:42.410 --> 00:45.778
DEAD WRONG.
GET OUT.

00:45.813 --> 00:46.812
OKAY, JENNIFER.

00:46.847 --> 00:48.781
MY NAME IS ALEX.

00:48.816 --> 00:50.949
UH, YEAH, WELL,
I KNOW THAT<i> NOW.</i>

00:50.985 --> 00:52.951
NOW YOU CAN LEAVE.

00:52.987 --> 00:55.888
YOU REALLY DON'T REMEMBER ME,
DO YOU?

00:55.923 --> 00:58.690
-MY NAME IS ALEX.
-JENNIFER.

00:58.726 --> 01:01.927
YOU SENT ME
THESE TEXT MESSAGES.

01:01.962 --> 01:03.662
I DON'T KNOW
WHO SENT YOU ANYTHING.

01:03.697 --> 01:05.264
IT WAS NOT ME.

01:05.299 --> 01:07.166
TH-THAT<i> WAS</i> YOU.

01:07.201 --> 01:08.967
WE MET.

01:09.003 --> 01:10.836
OH, MY GOODNESS.
COME ON.

01:10.871 --> 01:13.138
COME ON, JENN-- OR ALEX
OR WH-WHATEVER YOUR NAME IS.

01:13.174 --> 01:14.907
LISTEN, WE'RE ADULTS.

01:14.942 --> 01:16.074
IF I WOULD'VE KNOWN
YOU WERE MARRIED,

01:16.110 --> 01:17.810
I WOULDN'T HAVE SAID
ANYTHING.

01:17.845 --> 01:19.144
I WAS MARRIED, TOO.

01:19.180 --> 01:23.081
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

01:23.117 --> 01:26.718
WE MET ONE AFTERNOON
FOR LUNCH AT THE MAXINE HOTEL.

01:26.754 --> 01:27.786
YOU WERE SO NERVOUS,

01:27.822 --> 01:29.521
YOU KEPT LOOKING OVER
YOUR SHOULDER.

01:29.557 --> 01:31.056
YOU WERE TELLING ME
ABOUT YOUR BREAKUP,

01:31.091 --> 01:32.991
AND YOU TOLD ME
YOUR NAME WAS JENNIFER.

01:33.027 --> 01:34.660
[ Chuckling ] OKAY.

01:34.695 --> 01:36.995
LOOK,
THIS WAS A MISTAKE.

01:37.031 --> 01:39.398
CLEARLY,
YOU ARE DRUNK.

01:39.433 --> 01:41.266
I DON'T KNOW WHO THAT HAPPENED
WITH, BUT IT WAS NOT WITH ME.

01:41.302 --> 01:42.401
IT NEVER HAPPENED.

01:42.436 --> 01:45.137
YOU NEED TO GO --
NOW.

01:45.172 --> 01:46.338
LOOK, I WOULD'VE NEVER
DONE ANYTHING

01:46.373 --> 01:47.406
IF I THOUGHT
IT WOULD UPSET YOU.

01:47.441 --> 01:48.407
I DIDN'T KNOW.

01:48.442 --> 01:50.075
YOU DON'T KNOW ME --
AT ALL.

01:50.110 --> 01:51.710
LOOK, JUST GIVE ME
THE DIVORCE PAPERS.

01:51.745 --> 01:52.711
NO, YOU DON'T...

01:52.746 --> 01:54.279
-NO, LISTEN.
-...NEED TO HELP ME.

01:54.315 --> 01:55.113
YOU DON'T NEED TO LOOK
AT THEM, REALLY.

01:55.149 --> 01:56.114
I WANT TO HELP YOU,
OKAY?

01:56.150 --> 01:57.516
I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T KNOW.

01:59.253 --> 02:01.687
[ SIGHS ]

02:01.722 --> 02:02.921
OKAY.

02:05.159 --> 02:08.060
I'LL TAKE THE DIVORCE PAPERS,
AND I -- AND I'M GOING HOME.

02:08.095 --> 02:13.966
♪♪

02:14.001 --> 02:19.371
♪♪

02:19.406 --> 02:20.839
ALL RIGHT, SO I'M GONNA JUST
TAKE A LOOK AT THESE,

02:20.875 --> 02:23.308
AND I'LL BRING THEM BACK
TOMORROW.

02:23.344 --> 02:25.744
JUST CALL ME
WITH WHATEVER ADVICE.

02:25.779 --> 02:26.945
YOU DON'T NEED
TO COME HERE.

02:26.981 --> 02:28.313
OKAY, FINE.

02:30.417 --> 02:32.217
I'M GOING NOW.

02:32.253 --> 02:34.586
FINE. JUST...

02:39.226 --> 02:40.626
GOODBYE.

02:40.661 --> 02:48.400
♪♪

02:48.435 --> 02:51.403
