www.vitac.com

02:51.438 --> 02:54.172
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

02:56.193 --> 02:58.961
WE TAKE ALL CALLS
VERY SERIOUSLY,

02:58.996 --> 03:01.563
SO I'LL HAVE SOMEBODY
RETURN YOUR CALL.

03:01.599 --> 03:04.800
I APPRECIATE
THE INFORMATION.

03:04.835 --> 03:07.336
THANK YOU.

03:07.371 --> 03:09.738
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

03:09.773 --> 03:11.173
BROUGHT YOU A COFFEE,
LOU.

03:11.208 --> 03:13.308
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

03:14.311 --> 03:16.645
YOU MUST BE A FOOL IF YOU THINK
THAT I'M GONNA DRINK THAT.

03:16.680 --> 03:18.113
COME ON, MAN,
I WAS TRYING TO BE NICE.

03:18.148 --> 03:19.748
CHEERS.

03:19.783 --> 03:21.049
[ CHUCKLES ] NO.

03:21.085 --> 03:22.718
NO, NO, NO.

03:22.753 --> 03:24.586
"NO, NO, NO," WHAT?

03:24.622 --> 03:27.623
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW TO BE NICE.
COME ON.

03:27.658 --> 03:30.392
[ SCOFFS ] SEE, MAN, I KNOW
WE'VE HAD OUR DIFFERENCES,

03:30.427 --> 03:34.263
BUT I'M JUST SITTING HERE
TRYING TO TALK WITH YOU.

03:34.298 --> 03:35.864
WHAT'S THIS?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

03:35.900 --> 03:37.165
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

03:37.201 --> 03:38.834
EVERY TIME I'M JUST BEING
A NORMAL, NICE GUY,

03:38.869 --> 03:39.935
YOU THINK
I'M UP TO SOMETHING.

03:39.970 --> 03:40.969
YOU'RE ALWAYS
QUESTIONING ME.

03:41.005 --> 03:43.405
NO.
'CAUSE YOU DON'T KNOW HOW TO.

03:43.440 --> 03:44.840
YOU'RE ALWAYS TRYING
TO RAISE HELL.

03:44.875 --> 03:46.308
I'M NOT TRYING
TO RAISE HELL.

03:46.343 --> 03:47.409
I'M JUST TRYING
TO TALK.

03:47.444 --> 03:48.877
CAN WE HAVE
A CONVERSATION?

03:48.913 --> 03:51.079
-ABOUT?
-OKAY, LOOK, MAN.

03:51.115 --> 03:52.481
NO SECRETS HERE ANYMORE.

03:52.516 --> 03:54.816
I KNOW YOU GUYS ARE FBI,
YOU KNOW I'M D.E.A.,

03:54.852 --> 03:57.452
WE'RE BOTH TRYING
TO TAKE DOWN THE CARTEL,

03:57.488 --> 03:58.954
BUT I KNOW YOU GUYS
ARE HIDING STUFF FROM US.

03:58.989 --> 04:00.022
[ SCOFFS ]

04:00.057 --> 04:01.089
WHY DON'T WE
JUST SHARE INFORMATION

04:01.125 --> 04:02.491
AND WORK TOWARDS
A COMMON GOAL?

04:02.526 --> 04:03.859
OKAY, I LIKE THAT.

04:03.894 --> 04:05.160
SHARE INFORMATION.

04:05.195 --> 04:06.395
WORK FOR
THE COMMON GOAL.

04:06.430 --> 04:08.697
ALL RIGHT,
YOU GO FIRST.

04:10.501 --> 04:11.366
OKAY.

04:11.402 --> 04:13.135
ALL RIGHT, WELL...

04:13.170 --> 04:14.269
WE KNOW THAT THEY'VE SET UP
IN MAXINE --

04:14.305 --> 04:15.437
OH, COME ON,
I'M NOT EVEN --

04:15.472 --> 04:16.471
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS,
ALL RIGHT.

04:16.507 --> 04:18.206
WHAT'S ALL THIS ABOUT?

04:18.242 --> 04:20.676
ALL RIGHT, LET ME
CUT TO THE POINT.

04:20.711 --> 04:23.145
WHY'D YOU STOP ASKING ME
ABOUT ANDREW?

04:23.180 --> 04:25.213
WHAT DO YOU MEAN "WHY"?

04:25.249 --> 04:27.082
I MEAN, ALL YOU KEPT DOING
IS RIDING ME ABOUT,

04:27.117 --> 04:28.550
"WHERE'S ANDREW,
WHERE'S ANDREW?"

04:28.585 --> 04:32.154
AND THEN ONE DAY, IT STOPPED,
AND YOU'RE NOT A QUITTER, LOU.

04:32.189 --> 04:34.923
YEAH,
AND WHAT'S YOUR POINT?

04:34.959 --> 04:37.726
SO DO YOU WANT TO TELL ME
WHERE HE IS?

04:37.761 --> 04:39.361
I DON'T KNOW.

04:39.396 --> 04:40.929
HE'S NOT IN PROTECTIVE CUSTODY,
IS HE?

04:40.965 --> 04:42.531
OH, COME ON,
I KNOW AS MUCH AS YOU DO.

04:42.566 --> 04:43.732
PROTECTIVE CUSTODY?

04:43.767 --> 04:45.434
WHAT -- WHAT --
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

04:45.469 --> 04:47.302
I'M TALKING ABOUT --
DID THE FBI

04:47.338 --> 04:49.371
PUT ANDREW
IN PROTECTIVE CUSTODY?

04:49.406 --> 04:50.906
I DON'T KNOW.
DID THEY?

04:50.941 --> 04:52.908
DID YOU?
QUIT SAYING "THEY."

04:52.943 --> 04:54.409
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

04:54.445 --> 04:55.711
OKAY.

04:55.746 --> 04:57.746
YOU JUST GONNA SIT HERE AND PLAY
THESE GAMES WITH ME, LOU?

04:57.781 --> 04:59.648
WHAT'S THE MATTER, HMM?

04:59.683 --> 05:02.284
YOU WORRIED ABOUT SOMETHING,
EDDIE?

05:02.319 --> 05:04.086
EDDIE AIN'T EVER WORRIED.

05:04.121 --> 05:05.620
WELL, THAT'S GOOD.

05:05.656 --> 05:07.255
GOOD.

05:07.291 --> 05:08.957
SO ANSWER THE QUESTION.

05:08.993 --> 05:10.959
WHY DID ALL THE SUDDEN
YOU JUST QUIT ASKING ME

05:10.995 --> 05:12.561
ABOUT ANDREW, LOU?

05:12.596 --> 05:14.796
YOU KNOW WHAT, I'LL HELP YOU.
I'LL DO ONE EVEN BETTER.

05:14.832 --> 05:19.034
LET ME JUST ASK YOU,
DO<i> YOU</i> KNOW WHERE ANDREW IS?

05:19.069 --> 05:20.369
OH, THAT'S CUTE.

05:20.404 --> 05:23.839
I HAVE NO IDEA WHERE THE GUY IS.
YOU KNOW THAT.

05:23.874 --> 05:25.207
YOU KNOW WHAT, MAN,
I CAME HERE,

05:25.242 --> 05:26.441
TRYING TO EXTEND
AN OLIVE BRANCH,

05:26.477 --> 05:28.510
BUT I SEE THAT AIN'T HAPPENING
WITH YOU.

05:28.545 --> 05:30.846
YOU STILL TRYING
TO TAKE ME OUT, LOU?

05:30.881 --> 05:33.582
WITH EVERYTHING
INSIDE OF ME.

05:33.617 --> 05:34.916
GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.

05:34.952 --> 05:36.218
ENJOY YOUR LATTE.

05:36.253 --> 05:38.453
OH. THANKS.

05:40.791 --> 05:42.891
THAT WAS $4.95,
YOU SON OF A BITCH.

05:46.930 --> 05:48.730
HEY.

05:51.935 --> 05:54.536
MAN, I HATE THAT GUY.

05:54.571 --> 05:56.405
JOIN THE CLUB.

05:57.274 --> 05:59.074
[ TAPS FOLDER ]

05:59.109 --> 06:01.610
I GOT SOMETHING.

06:01.645 --> 06:02.878
WHAT'S THIS?

06:02.913 --> 06:05.714
I SPOKE TO MARGARET AGAIN,
AND SHE GAVE ME THAT.

06:08.619 --> 06:10.419
WHO ARE ALL THESE WOMEN?

06:10.454 --> 06:13.055
ALL THE WOMAN
THE CHURCH TRIED TO HIDE.

06:13.090 --> 06:15.457
THEY WERE BEING STALKED.

06:15.492 --> 06:16.525
OH.

06:16.560 --> 06:17.726
YEAH.

06:17.761 --> 06:20.429
EXACTLY WHAT WE NEED.

06:20.464 --> 06:22.597
WILL THEY TALK?

06:22.633 --> 06:24.099
THAT'S THE ONLY THING.

06:24.134 --> 06:25.434
THEY'RE AFRAID TO.

06:25.469 --> 06:27.936
HMM, AH, YOU KNOW WHAT?

06:27.971 --> 06:29.471
IT SHOULD BE ENOUGH.

06:29.506 --> 06:31.306
-YEAH?
-YEAH.

06:33.277 --> 06:34.609
I'M GONNA GO TELL KELLY.

06:34.645 --> 06:36.511
DON-- NO, NO, NO, NO.

06:36.547 --> 06:37.813
DON'T TELL HER TOO MUCH.

06:37.848 --> 06:38.947
NO, I'M NOT --
I MEAN, NOT LIKE THAT.

06:38.982 --> 06:40.148
I'M JUST GONNA TELL HER
WE GOT SOMETHING

06:40.184 --> 06:42.084
AND WE GOT SOMETHING GOOD.

06:42.119 --> 06:44.286
ALL RIGHT.
OKAY.

06:44.321 --> 06:47.255
HEY, REALLY APPRECIATE
YOU GETTING THIS.

06:47.291 --> 06:50.025
THANKS, MAN.
I THINK IT'S GONNA WORK.

06:50.060 --> 06:52.227
I THINK SO, TOO.

06:52.262 --> 06:54.096
GREAT WORK.
-THANK YOU, MAN.

06:54.131 --> 06:56.064
WE'RE GONNA GET HER OFF.

06:56.100 --> 06:57.132
WE WILL.

06:57.167 --> 06:58.266
THAT'S RIGHT.
WE'RE GONNA TRY.

06:58.302 --> 07:03.738
♪♪

07:03.774 --> 07:08.677
♪♪

07:08.712 --> 07:11.746
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS,
Ringing ]

07:11.782 --> 07:13.682
-Hello. Ian Glenn.
-IAN.

07:13.717 --> 07:15.917
-HEY.
-We got something.

07:15.953 --> 07:16.852
TELL ME.

07:16.887 --> 07:18.620
I GOT OVER NINE WOMEN

07:18.655 --> 07:20.322
AND PROOF
THAT THE CHURCH SETTLED

07:20.357 --> 07:22.190
AFTER THEY BROUGHT
ALLEGATIONS.

07:22.226 --> 07:23.291
HOW'D YOU GET THAT?

07:23.327 --> 07:24.593
EH, WE GOT IT.

07:24.628 --> 07:26.194
OKAY.

07:26.230 --> 07:28.130
WAIT, DON'T YOU WANT TO KNOW
IF IT'S LEGIT?

07:28.165 --> 07:30.999
LOOK, I ALREADY KNOW
IT'S LEGIT, BUT IT'S TOO CLOSE.

07:31.034 --> 07:32.100
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

07:32.136 --> 07:33.235
WHAT --
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

07:33.270 --> 07:35.237
IT'S TOO CLOSE.

07:35.272 --> 07:36.671
LOOK,
IF WE GO DOWN THAT ROAD,

07:36.707 --> 07:38.673
LARRY AND THE GUYS AT THE FIRM
ALREADY THINK IT'S ME.

07:38.709 --> 07:39.774
SO WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

07:39.810 --> 07:41.476
I'M SAYING IT'S TOO CLOSE.

07:41.512 --> 07:43.712
LOOK, YOU SAID TO COME UP
WITH THE EVIDENCE.

07:43.747 --> 07:45.280
LOOK, MAN, I'M STILL IN,
ALL RIGHT?

07:45.315 --> 07:48.150
I'M STILL IN.
I JUST GOT TO THINK THIS OUT.

07:48.185 --> 07:49.551
UH [CLEARS THROAT]

07:49.586 --> 07:52.120
IAN, YOU KNOW, I AM TRYING
TO TRUST YOU HERE,

07:52.156 --> 07:53.388
SO YOU NEED TO BE
STRAIGHT UP WITH ME.

07:53.423 --> 07:55.724
YEAH, I'M IN, MAN,
I'M IN, ALL RIGHT.

07:55.759 --> 07:57.926
JUST GIVE ME SOME TIME.
I-I GOT TO FIGURE IT OUT.

07:57.961 --> 08:00.295
ALL RIGHT, SO WHAT DO WE DO?
'CAUSE I WANT HER OUT OF THERE.

08:00.330 --> 08:01.730
[ Sighs ]
Yeah, I get that, man.

08:01.765 --> 08:03.899
HEY, LOOK, LET ME CALL YOU AFTER
I GET OUT OF COURT, ALL RIGHT?

08:03.934 --> 08:05.333
I JUST GOT TO FIGURE IT OUT.

08:05.369 --> 08:07.235
-OKAY.
-Hey.

08:07.271 --> 08:08.570
YEAH?

08:08.605 --> 08:09.971
HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW ALEX?

08:10.007 --> 08:11.339
WELL. WHY?

08:11.375 --> 08:13.975
IS SHE THE TYPE OF WOMAN
TO STEP OUT ON HER HUSBAND?

08:14.011 --> 08:15.277
LOOK, SHE'S GOING THROUGH
A DIVORCE.

08:15.312 --> 08:17.512
ARE YOU ASKING ME
IF SHE'S, LIKE, AVAILABLE?

08:17.548 --> 08:19.981
NO, NO, NO.
NO, NO, NOT -- NOT AT ALL.

08:20.017 --> 08:21.650
THEN WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

08:21.685 --> 08:24.319
[ SIGHS ]
I WAS JUST WONDERING.

08:24.354 --> 08:25.720
WHY?

08:25.756 --> 08:27.155
HEY, LOOK, MAN, I GOT TO GO
TO COURT, ALL RIGHT.

08:27.191 --> 08:28.723
LET ME -- LET ME TA--
TALK TO YOU LATER.

08:28.759 --> 08:30.258
UH, WHAT --
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

08:30.294 --> 08:31.760
LOOK, I'LL TELL YOU LATER,
OKAY?

08:31.795 --> 08:34.362
ALL RIGHT.
OH, ALSO, ALSO, UM...

08:34.398 --> 08:37.365
CAN YOU CALL THAT KID?
THE LAWYER?

08:37.401 --> 08:39.401
HAVE HIM COME OVER TO MY HOUSE
SO WE CAN, UH --

08:39.436 --> 08:40.502
so we can
work things out.

08:40.537 --> 08:42.137
YEAH, I'M ON IT.

08:42.172 --> 08:43.305
Tonight.

08:43.340 --> 08:44.439
I'M ON IT, LUSHION.

08:44.474 --> 08:45.907
ALL RIGHT, THANKS.

08:45.943 --> 08:47.275
ALL RIGHT, BYE.

08:51.081 --> 08:53.615
[ CELLPHONE CLICKING, BEEPS ]

08:53.650 --> 08:56.184
[ SIGHS ]

08:56.220 --> 08:57.552
HEY, CARL.

08:57.588 --> 08:59.120
YEAH, THIS IS IAN GLENN.

08:59.156 --> 09:01.356
I WANT TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT A CASE.

09:01.391 --> 09:04.559
HEY, LISTEN, THIS HAS TO STAY
VERY PRIVATE.

09:04.595 --> 09:07.062
YEAH, YEAH, I KN-- I KNOW
YOU MET WITH KELLY ISSACS.

09:07.097 --> 09:09.297
YES, IT'S ABOUT HER.

09:09.333 --> 09:11.032
OKAY, LISTEN.

09:11.068 --> 09:13.134
LISTEN, MAN,
DON'T TELL A SOUL.

09:13.170 --> 09:15.637
ALL RIGHT, I'M-A TEXT YOU
IN A FEW HOURS WITH THE ADDRESS.

09:15.672 --> 09:17.472
ALL RIGHT,
SEE YOU THEN, CARL.

09:20.427 --> 09:24.763
♪♪

09:24.798 --> 09:27.232
HEY.

09:27.267 --> 09:29.768
I BROUGHT YOU SOMETHING.

09:29.803 --> 09:31.336
WHAT'S THAT?

09:31.371 --> 09:33.305
SOME PUDDING.

09:33.340 --> 09:35.140
THANKS.

09:38.011 --> 09:41.246
YOU KNOW, IF IT DOESN'T HAVE
A KEY OUT OF HERE,

09:41.281 --> 09:43.181
IT MAY NOT TASTE
AS SWEET.

09:43.216 --> 09:46.084
THAT'S WHAT --
WE GOT IT.

09:46.119 --> 09:47.452
WHAT?

09:47.487 --> 09:50.555
FOUND OUT THERE WAS SEVERAL
OTHER WOMEN AT THE CHURCH.

09:50.590 --> 09:52.324
REALLY?
HOW MANY?

09:52.359 --> 09:53.925
A LOT.

09:53.961 --> 09:55.727
BUT THEY'RE AFRAID TO TALK,
THOUGH.

09:55.762 --> 09:56.895
WHY?

09:56.930 --> 09:58.730
YOU KNOW
HOW THE CHURCH IS.

10:01.802 --> 10:04.002
SO I COULD JUST BE
STUCK IN HERE?

10:04.037 --> 10:05.370
NO.

10:05.405 --> 10:07.072
YOU GOT LUSHION
TALKING TO THE LAWYER,

10:07.107 --> 10:09.107
AND THEY'RE BOTH
GONNA TALK TO THE D.A.

10:09.142 --> 10:11.343
ARE YOU SURE?

10:11.378 --> 10:13.478
YEAH.

10:13.513 --> 10:16.114
SO THERE'S A CHANCE THAT
THEY MIGHT KNOW I'M NOT LYING?

10:16.149 --> 10:17.949
YEAH, YEAH.

10:17.985 --> 10:20.819
[ EXHALES HEAVILY ]
THANK YOU, GOD.

10:20.854 --> 10:23.855
YEAH.

10:23.890 --> 10:25.590
SO HOW LONG IS THIS
ALL GONNA TAKE?

10:25.625 --> 10:27.692
LOOK, KELLY,
I DON'T KNOW, OKAY?

10:27.728 --> 10:29.394
-RICK.
-IT'S NOT GONNA BE LONG.

10:29.429 --> 10:31.229
WE'RE WORKING ON IT.

10:35.469 --> 10:38.236
THANKS FOR THE PUDDING.

10:38.271 --> 10:42.440
YEAH, AND, UH, THANK YOU
FOR NOT HATING ME.

10:42.476 --> 10:43.942
WHY WOULD I HATE YOU?

10:43.977 --> 10:45.210
'CAUSE I
DIDN'T DO THIS SOONER.

10:45.245 --> 10:47.579
I SHOULD'VE BELIEVED YOU
EARLIER.

10:47.614 --> 10:49.147
YOU DIDN'T KNOW.

10:49.182 --> 10:50.415
BUT I<i> SHOULD'VE</i> KNOWN.

10:50.450 --> 10:52.650
I'M AN OFFICER,
YOU KNOW?

10:52.686 --> 10:55.754
YEAH, WELL,
I SLEPT WITH HIM.

10:55.789 --> 10:57.155
I SHOULD'VE KNOWN.
-YEAH, YOU DID.

10:57.190 --> 10:58.323
-[ CHUCKLES ]
-BUT -- BUT THAT'S OVER.

10:58.358 --> 10:59.424
THAT'S OVER NOW, SO...

10:59.459 --> 11:01.192
-NO, IT'S NOT.
-YES, IT IS.

11:01.228 --> 11:04.095
LOOK AT ME, RICK.
I'M IN JAIL.

11:04.131 --> 11:05.530
LOOK, THIS IS
NOT GONNA BE LONG.

11:05.565 --> 11:08.133
I'M GONNA GET YOU
OUT OF HERE.

11:08.168 --> 11:09.534
I LOVE YOUR CONFIDENCE.

11:09.569 --> 11:11.603
IT'S --
IT'S JUST HOW I FEEL.

11:11.638 --> 11:14.639
SO IS THAT THE ONLY REASON
WHY YOU'RE BEING SO NICE TO ME?

11:17.044 --> 11:18.943
LOOK, I'M AN OFFICER
OF THE LAW, OKAY?

11:18.979 --> 11:20.445
I GOT TO DO WHAT'S RIGHT.

11:20.480 --> 11:23.181
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

11:23.216 --> 11:25.250
OKAY.

11:25.285 --> 11:26.818
THANK YOU AGAIN.

11:26.853 --> 11:28.653
SURE. AND IF YOU, UH --
YOU LIKE WHAT I BROUGHT YOU --

11:28.688 --> 11:30.588
YOUR TREAT --
THAT PUDDING --

11:30.624 --> 11:32.524
THEN YOU CAN, UH --
YOU CAN ALWAYS HIT ME UP.

11:32.559 --> 11:34.292
I'M RIGHT AROUND THE CORNER.
-OKAY.

11:34.327 --> 11:36.428
I THINK I'M GOOD, BUT...

11:36.463 --> 11:37.996
ALL RIGHT.
-OKAY.

11:38.031 --> 11:40.632
I'LL KEEP YOU POSTED,
OKAY?

11:40.667 --> 11:43.268
THANK YOU, RICK.

11:43.303 --> 11:44.969
SURE.

11:45.005 --> 11:47.405
I'LL BE BACK, ALL RIGHT?

11:47.441 --> 11:48.640
YEAH.

11:48.675 --> 11:54.212
♪♪

11:54.247 --> 11:56.047
[ SIGHS ]

11:56.083 --> 11:58.116
OKAY, I GUESS I'LL SEE YOU
IN THE MORNING, THEN.

11:58.151 --> 11:59.217
YEP.

11:59.252 --> 12:00.985
THAT'S A LITTLE BIT
TOO SOON, HUH?

12:01.021 --> 12:10.395
♪♪

12:10.430 --> 12:12.530
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

12:14.634 --> 12:16.634
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
HELLO?

12:16.670 --> 12:18.269
Hey, it's Dr. Raston.

12:18.305 --> 12:19.604
OH, HI.

12:19.639 --> 12:22.273
Just wanted to be sure
you would be on time.

12:22.309 --> 12:24.008
UH, YES, YES,
I WILL.

12:24.044 --> 12:25.677
Okay. Thank you.

12:25.712 --> 12:26.711
OF COURSE.

12:26.746 --> 12:28.646
Okay, I will see you
when you get here.

12:28.682 --> 12:31.249
YEP, I'LL SEE YOU SOON.
BYE.

12:31.284 --> 12:32.851
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

12:32.886 --> 12:35.019
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

12:35.055 --> 12:37.088
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

12:37.124 --> 12:38.923
HI.
-Hi.

12:38.959 --> 12:41.860
I JUST WANTED TO REMIND YOU
THAT I'LL BE OVER TODAY

12:41.895 --> 12:44.028
so that you can sign
those divorce papers.

12:44.064 --> 12:46.664
[ SIGHS ] BRAD, LOOK,
I-I HAVEN'T EVEN HAD A CHANCE

12:46.700 --> 12:48.666
TO HAVE THE LAWYER
LOOK THEM OVER YET THIS MORNING.

12:48.702 --> 12:49.801
OH, COME ON, ALEX.

12:49.836 --> 12:51.669
I GAVE YOU 24 HOURS.
-I know.

12:51.705 --> 12:53.438
LOOK, I'M GOING TO SIGN THEM,
OKAY?

12:53.473 --> 12:55.106
I-I PROMISE.
DON'T WORRY.

12:55.142 --> 12:57.242
NOTHING'S CHANGING
IN THOSE PAPERS, ALEX,

12:57.277 --> 12:58.810
SO YOU MIGHT AS WELL
JUST SIGN THEM.

12:58.845 --> 13:00.545
I WILL, UM,
BUT THERE'S SOMETHING

13:00.580 --> 13:01.880
I HAVE TO TELL YOU FIRST,
OKAY?

13:01.915 --> 13:04.849
[ SIGHS ] I DON'T REALLY CARE
WHAT YOU HAVE TO SAY.

13:04.885 --> 13:06.751
Brad, please, just listen.

13:06.786 --> 13:08.219
THE BABY ISN'T RANDAL'S.

13:08.255 --> 13:10.355
[ SIGHS, LAUGHS ]

13:12.292 --> 13:14.459
YOU -- YOU REALLY EXPECT ME
TO BELIEVE THAT?

13:14.494 --> 13:16.060
I-I THINK HE MIGHT BE YOURS.

13:16.096 --> 13:18.463
YOU ARE OUT OF YOUR MIND,
ALEX.

13:18.498 --> 13:20.765
[ SIGHS ]
LOOK, I'M TELLING YOU, PLEASE.

13:20.800 --> 13:22.700
THERE'S NO WAY THAT BABY
IS MINE.

13:22.736 --> 13:24.769
Listen,
I'm telling you the truth.

13:24.804 --> 13:28.139
OKAY, D-DR. RASTON SAID
THAT SOMETIMES GENES CAN --

13:28.175 --> 13:31.643
CAN SKIP A FEW GENERATIONS,
AND -- AND MAYBE HE --

13:31.678 --> 13:35.146
THERE IS NO ONE IN MY FAMILY
WITH THAT ETHNICITY,

13:35.182 --> 13:36.247
AND YOU KNOW THAT.

13:36.283 --> 13:37.649
I MEAN, ARE YOU SURE?

13:37.684 --> 13:39.050
YES.
OF COURSE I'M SURE.

13:39.085 --> 13:40.852
What kind of game
are you playing, Alex?

13:40.887 --> 13:42.620
COULD YOU PLEASE JUST --
JUST CALL YOUR PARENTS

13:42.656 --> 13:44.422
AND ASK THEM
AND JUST DOUBLE CHECK?

13:44.457 --> 13:45.423
THIS IS INSANE.

13:45.458 --> 13:47.592
BRAD, THE BABY ISN'T RANDAL'S.

13:47.627 --> 13:49.060
IT HAS TO BE YOURS.

13:49.095 --> 13:50.828
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND
OR SOMETHING?

13:50.864 --> 13:52.664
WHAT IS SHE SAYING?

13:52.699 --> 13:53.731
NO.

13:53.767 --> 13:55.433
Listen, I'll be
over there tonight,

13:55.468 --> 13:57.001
AND YOU BETTER SIGN
THOSE PAPERS.

13:57.037 --> 13:58.603
BRAD, PLEASE,
I'M -- I'M TELLING YOU.

13:58.638 --> 13:59.971
Please --
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

14:00.006 --> 14:02.240
WHA--
WHAT WAS THAT ALL ABOUT?

14:02.275 --> 14:04.709
SHE SAYS THAT I'M THE FATHER
OF THAT BABY.

14:04.744 --> 14:06.844
WHAT?
WHY WOULD SHE SAY THAT?

14:06.880 --> 14:08.980
THE DNA TEST SAYS
THAT RANDAL'S NOT THE FATHER.

14:09.015 --> 14:10.548
-NO WAY.
-THAT'S WHAT SHE'S SAYING.

14:10.584 --> 14:12.016
BUT SHE SAID RANDAL
WAS THE FATHER,

14:12.052 --> 14:13.685
AND THEY SWITCHED
THE TESTS?

14:13.720 --> 14:15.787
I DON'T CARE, MARCIE.
I JUST -- I JUST WANT A DIVORCE.

14:15.822 --> 14:17.121
SHE'S OUT
OF HER DAMN MIND.

14:17.157 --> 14:19.390
WELL, YES, SHE IS.

14:19.426 --> 14:20.658
DAMN IT.

14:20.694 --> 14:22.493
IT'S ONE THING AFTER ANOTHER,
THIS GIRL.

14:22.529 --> 14:24.095
I KNOW.
JUST RELAX, OKAY?

14:24.130 --> 14:26.130
DON'T -- DON'T LET IT
STRESS YOU OUT.

14:26.166 --> 14:27.765
I JUST WANT TO BE FREE.
THAT'S ALL.

14:27.801 --> 14:29.534
I KNOW, I KNOW.

14:29.569 --> 14:31.369
YOU WILL, OKAY?

14:31.404 --> 14:33.204
YOU'RE ALMOST THERE.

14:34.541 --> 14:37.141
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

14:37.177 --> 14:38.977
JUST A SECOND.

14:45.552 --> 14:49.787
♪♪

14:49.823 --> 14:51.155
HI.

14:51.191 --> 14:52.523
HI.

14:52.559 --> 14:53.958
ARE YOU BUSY?

14:53.994 --> 14:56.628
UH, NO.

14:56.663 --> 14:58.696
CAN I COME IN?

14:58.732 --> 14:59.864
UH...

14:59.899 --> 15:02.300
LOOK, I PROMISE,
WHATEVER HAPPENED LAST NIGHT,

15:02.335 --> 15:04.369
IT WON'T HAPPEN AGAIN.
ALL RIGHT?

15:04.404 --> 15:08.940
I WAS DRUNK,
AND I'M VERY, VERY SORRY.

15:08.975 --> 15:10.775
I WAS SO WRONG
ABOUT YOU.

15:14.481 --> 15:15.580
COME IN.

15:15.615 --> 15:17.415
THANK YOU.

15:20.053 --> 15:21.853
UH...

15:24.591 --> 15:27.525
♪♪

15:27.560 --> 15:28.693
UM...

15:28.728 --> 15:30.895
DID YOU GET A CHANCE
TO LOOK AT THE PAPERS?

15:30.930 --> 15:32.764
YES, I DID.

15:32.799 --> 15:34.632
IT'S PRETTY MUCH
GIVING HIM EVERYTHING.

15:34.668 --> 15:35.833
EXCEPT FOR THE HOUSE.

15:35.869 --> 15:38.636
YOU DO KEEP THE HOUSE
AND 50% OF HIS INCOME.

15:38.672 --> 15:41.039
AND YOU GET JOINT CUSTODY
OF TWO OF THE KIDS.

15:41.074 --> 15:42.940
IS THAT
WHAT YOU WANTED?

15:42.976 --> 15:44.976
YES. YEAH.
THAT'S FINE.

15:45.011 --> 15:46.978
ARE YOU SURE?
YOU COULD GET MORE.

15:47.013 --> 15:48.346
NO, I-I DON'T WANT MORE.

15:48.381 --> 15:51.949
JUST WHAT'S FAIR,
AND HE'S BEING FAIR, SO...

15:51.985 --> 15:54.719
BUT HE'S ONLY PROVIDING CHILD
SUPPORT FOR TWO OF THE KIDS.

15:54.754 --> 15:56.587
WELL, UH...

15:56.623 --> 15:58.189
WHY IS THAT?

15:58.224 --> 16:00.091
IT'S FINE, REALLY.

16:00.126 --> 16:01.492
I MEAN, HE REALLY
SHOULD BE PROVIDING

16:01.528 --> 16:02.727
CHILD SUPPORT
FOR ALL THREE.

16:02.762 --> 16:05.963
NO, IT'S FINE.

16:05.999 --> 16:07.932
OKAY.

16:07.967 --> 16:09.467
THANK YOU
FOR LOOKING THEM OVER.

16:09.502 --> 16:10.501
I'LL SIGN THEM.

16:10.537 --> 16:13.538
YEAH, YOU CAN SIGN
RIGHT HERE.

16:13.573 --> 16:15.673
AND IF YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND
AND YOU WANT TO GO FOR MORE,

16:15.709 --> 16:17.942
JUST LET ME KNOW.

16:17.977 --> 16:20.678
I-I DON'T.
THANK YOU.

16:20.714 --> 16:23.781
AND, LOOK, I'M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT LAST NIGHT.

16:23.817 --> 16:25.883
PLEASE FORGIVE ME.

16:25.919 --> 16:27.418
IT'S FINE.

16:27.454 --> 16:28.986
OKAY.

16:29.022 --> 16:30.521
-THANK YOU AGAIN.
-YOU'RE WELCOME.

16:30.557 --> 16:31.756
-REALLY.
-BYE.

16:31.791 --> 16:32.757
BYE.

16:32.792 --> 16:38.463
♪♪

16:38.498 --> 16:43.301
♪♪

16:43.336 --> 16:45.303
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:45.338 --> 16:50.341
♪♪

16:54.381 --> 16:56.147
Bennett: HEY, NEIGHBOR.

16:56.182 --> 16:57.115
HEY.

16:57.150 --> 16:58.750
HOW ARE YOU?

16:58.785 --> 17:01.652
GOOD. YOU KNOW, I -- I --
I NEEDED TO TALK TO YOU.

17:01.688 --> 17:03.121
OH?
WHAT HAPPENED?

17:03.156 --> 17:04.622
WELL, NOTHING.

17:04.657 --> 17:06.958
IT'S JUST --
IT'S YOUR WIFE.

17:06.993 --> 17:09.494
WHAT IS IT?

17:09.529 --> 17:14.098
WELL [SIGHS]
SHE WAS SAYING THAT RANDAL --

17:14.134 --> 17:15.400
THE NEIGHBOR?

17:15.435 --> 17:16.768
YEAH.

17:16.803 --> 17:18.503
YEAH, HE, UM...

17:18.538 --> 17:21.539
LOOK, HE WAS LOOKING
INTO YOUR HOUSE.

17:21.574 --> 17:23.674
WHAT --
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

17:23.710 --> 17:25.943
I WAS ON MY WAY
TO THE STORE,

17:25.979 --> 17:31.516
AND I SAW HIM LOOKING INTO
YOUR HOUSE WITH BINOCULARS.

17:31.551 --> 17:32.884
REALLY?

17:32.919 --> 17:36.487
YEAH. YEAH.

17:36.523 --> 17:39.290
I WANTED TO LET YOU KNOW.

17:39.325 --> 17:40.525
THANK YOU.

17:40.560 --> 17:42.093
YOU KNOW, MAYBE YOU SHOULD
CLOSE THE CURTAINS.

17:42.128 --> 17:43.494
CAN'T.

17:43.530 --> 17:44.962
SHE LIKES THE LIGHT.

17:46.433 --> 17:48.032
OKAY.

17:48.067 --> 17:50.168
I'LL TALK TO HIM.

17:50.203 --> 17:52.670
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S GONNA DO ANY GOOD.

17:52.705 --> 17:54.472
WELL, I DON'T KNOW.

17:54.507 --> 17:55.907
I CAN BE
PRETTY CONVINCING.

17:55.942 --> 17:58.709
YEAH, WELL, I'VE NEVER KNOWN
ANYONE WHO COULD STOP HIM.

17:58.745 --> 18:01.913
WELL, YOU'VE NEVER MET ME.

18:01.948 --> 18:04.148
NO, I HAVEN'T.

18:04.184 --> 18:05.883
-THANK YOU FOR TELLING ME.
-YEAH.

18:05.919 --> 18:08.820
HEY, YOU KNOW, I COULD ALWAYS
GET LUSHION TO TALK TO HIM.

18:08.855 --> 18:10.521
NO.

18:10.557 --> 18:12.290
PLEASE.

18:12.325 --> 18:14.525
LET ME.

18:14.561 --> 18:15.960
OKAY.

18:15.995 --> 18:17.428
THANK YOU.

18:17.464 --> 18:18.362
ALL RIGHT.

18:18.398 --> 18:19.831
YOU HAVE A GOOD DAY.

18:19.866 --> 18:21.065
-ALL RIGHT. TAKE CARE.
-YOU, TOO.

18:21.100 --> 18:22.767
ALL RIGHT.

18:22.802 --> 18:30.208
♪♪

18:30.243 --> 18:32.276
-HEY.
-HI.

18:32.312 --> 18:33.778
HOW ARE YOU?

18:33.813 --> 18:35.313
I'M GOOD.

18:35.348 --> 18:37.014
GOOD.

18:37.050 --> 18:43.721
♪♪

18:43.756 --> 18:46.624
THAT'S...BEAUTIFUL.

18:48.394 --> 18:49.427
YOU LIKE IT?

18:49.462 --> 18:51.262
I'VE BEEN WORKING ON IT
ALL DAY.

18:53.433 --> 18:55.833
I LOVE IT.

18:55.869 --> 18:57.969
THE COLORS ARE SO NICE.

18:58.004 --> 18:59.670
YEAH, THEY ARE.

18:59.706 --> 19:06.043
♪♪

19:06.079 --> 19:08.312
WHAT IS THIS?

19:08.348 --> 19:09.780
WHAT, YOU MEAN THE MAN?

19:09.816 --> 19:11.282
A MAN IN THE WINDOW.

19:11.317 --> 19:12.617
OH.

19:12.652 --> 19:15.553
HE'S JUST LOOKING AT THE GIRL
ACROSS THE STREET.

19:15.588 --> 19:19.891
SO, UM,
DID THIS REALLY HAPPEN?

19:19.926 --> 19:21.492
WHAT?

19:21.528 --> 19:23.761
WHAT'S, UH, IN YOUR PAINTING --
DID IT REALLY HAPPEN?

19:23.796 --> 19:26.330
NO.

19:26.366 --> 19:29.534
OKAY.

19:29.569 --> 19:30.501
WHY IS HE NAKED?

19:30.537 --> 19:31.936
HE JUST IS.

19:31.971 --> 19:35.239
OKAY.

19:35.275 --> 19:36.541
SO, ARE YOU HUNGRY?

19:36.576 --> 19:39.176
I MADE DINNER.

19:39.212 --> 19:40.845
YEAH.

19:40.880 --> 19:42.947
OKAY, I'LL GO
WARM IT UP FOR YOU.

19:42.982 --> 19:44.248
OKAY.

19:44.284 --> 19:51.022
♪♪

19:51.057 --> 19:52.323
HEY, BABE?

19:52.358 --> 19:53.157
MM-HMM?

19:53.192 --> 19:54.625
I, UH...

19:54.661 --> 19:56.193
I THINK I, UH,
FORGOT SOMETHING IN THE CAR.

19:56.229 --> 19:57.595
I'M GONNA BE
RIGHT BACK, OKAY?

19:57.630 --> 19:59.196
OKAY.

19:59.232 --> 20:08.706
♪♪

20:08.741 --> 20:18.249
♪♪

