♪♪

22:10.296 --> 22:11.862
AHH!

22:14.801 --> 22:17.835
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
UM...

22:17.870 --> 22:21.672
DR. RASTON
DID NOT SWITCH THE DNA.

22:21.708 --> 22:23.074
IT WAS TOTALLY ME.

22:23.109 --> 22:24.975
UM...

22:25.011 --> 22:27.344
I LIED TO COVER SOMETHING
THAT I HAD DONE.

22:27.380 --> 22:29.480
Doctor: WILL YOU TESTIFY TO THAT
IN COURT?

22:31.851 --> 22:33.050
YES.

22:33.086 --> 22:35.486
AND SHE'S ALSO SIGNED
AN AFFIDAVIT.

22:37.657 --> 22:39.256
OKAY.

22:39.292 --> 22:41.425
WE'VE HEARD ENOUGH.

22:41.461 --> 22:43.260
BRING IN MR. HOLMES,
PLEASE.

22:45.331 --> 22:46.764
WAIT, NO.

22:46.799 --> 22:48.499
I HAD NO IDEA THAT HE WAS
GOING TO BE HERE.

22:48.534 --> 22:50.134
HE HAD TO BE A PART
OF THE HEARING.

22:50.169 --> 22:51.135
NO.

22:51.170 --> 22:52.937
WAIT, NO.
-OKAY, ALEX. ALEX, PLEASE.

22:52.972 --> 22:54.638
ENOUGH.
OKAY?

22:54.674 --> 23:00.344
♪♪

23:00.379 --> 23:03.047
Randal: THIS IS MY LAWYER,
LARRY CONNLEE.

23:03.082 --> 23:06.517
PLEASE HAVE A SEAT.

23:06.552 --> 23:08.853
Y'ALL ABOUT TO FIRE
THIS BITCH

23:08.888 --> 23:11.689
FOR ALL THE PAIN
AND SUFFERING SHE CAUSED ME.

23:11.724 --> 23:14.425
MR. HOLMES,
WE, THIS BOARD,

23:14.460 --> 23:17.528
ARE SATISFIED DR. RASTON
DID NOTHING INAPPROPRIATE.

23:20.066 --> 23:21.532
THEN WHO THE HELL
SWITCHED IT?

23:21.567 --> 23:23.234
IT WASN'T SWITCHED.

23:23.269 --> 23:28.639
♪♪

23:28.674 --> 23:30.474
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

23:32.678 --> 23:34.478
HE'S NOT AWARE?

23:37.984 --> 23:40.317
ALEX.

23:40.353 --> 23:42.520
HAVE YOU NOT TOLD HIM?

23:42.555 --> 23:43.854
TELL HIM.

23:43.890 --> 23:45.222
I...

23:45.258 --> 23:46.690
YOU NEED TO EXPLAIN THIS
TO HIM.

23:46.726 --> 23:48.492
PLEASE TELL HIM.

23:50.997 --> 23:52.930
MR. HOLMES,

23:52.965 --> 23:56.367
WE HAD
THREE REMAINING SAMPLES.

23:56.402 --> 23:58.169
NO ONE SWITCHED THE DNA.

23:58.204 --> 24:03.741
♪♪

24:03.776 --> 24:06.377
WHAT THE HELL WENT WRONG?

24:06.412 --> 24:10.281
THERE IS NO WAY THAT YOU CAN BE
THAT CHILD'S BIOLOGICAL FATHER.

24:12.051 --> 24:14.151
[ LAUGHING ]

24:18.157 --> 24:19.857
BUT YOU --
YOU SEE WHAT I'M --

24:19.892 --> 24:21.292
YOU SEE WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT, THOUGH?

24:21.327 --> 24:23.494
[ CHUCKLES ] SEE?

24:23.529 --> 24:25.563
THIS IS WHY I'M SUING
THE HELL OUT OF THIS PLACE.

24:25.598 --> 24:27.498
'CAUSE Y'ALL LYING.
YOU'RE LYING.

24:27.533 --> 24:28.766
I'M SORRY.

24:28.801 --> 24:30.768
YOU ARE WELCOME TO TAKE
THE CHILD TO YOUR OWN DOCTOR

24:30.803 --> 24:33.904
AND/OR LAB
AND HAVE THE RESULTS REDONE.

24:33.940 --> 24:35.005
-WHAT?
-HOLD ON, RANDAL.

24:35.041 --> 24:36.941
CAN I SEE THOSE, PLEASE?

24:36.976 --> 24:38.809
-OF COURSE.
-THANK YOU.

24:38.845 --> 24:40.211
MM-HMM.

24:40.246 --> 24:42.179
THIS IS MY KID.

24:42.215 --> 24:44.715
I KNOW IT.

24:44.750 --> 24:45.916
SHE KNOWS IT.

24:45.952 --> 24:48.152
UH, RANDAL...

24:48.187 --> 24:49.486
WHAT?

24:49.522 --> 24:51.422
LOOK, I'VE NEVER KNOWN
A HOSPITAL

24:51.457 --> 24:54.258
