-[ LAUGHING ]

26:20.746 --> 26:22.446
Dr. Raston: YOU OKAY?

26:26.018 --> 26:27.818
-YES.
-OKAY.

26:30.640 --> 26:33.374
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

26:33.409 --> 26:35.142
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
HELLO?

26:35.177 --> 26:37.511
HI.
UH, THIS IS ESPERANZA.

26:37.546 --> 26:39.079
OH, YEAH, HI.

26:39.115 --> 26:41.348
HI. LISTEN, I-I'VE BEEN TRYING
TO REACH YOU.

26:41.384 --> 26:44.118
YEAH, YEAH. FOR SURE.
I'VE GOT YOU ON MY CALL CHAIN.

26:44.153 --> 26:46.353
OKAY,
WELL, LISTEN, I --

26:46.389 --> 26:50.457
I REALLY WANT TO GET
THESE PAPERS FILED, SO...

26:50.493 --> 26:51.825
GREAT.

26:51.861 --> 26:54.495
I'M NOT ACTUALLY IN MY OFFICE
RIGHT NOW, BUT, UM,

26:54.530 --> 26:56.997
I CAN SEND A CLERK DOWN THERE
TO FILE THEM FOR YOU.

26:57.033 --> 26:58.966
I WILL NEED TO BE PRESENT
TO SIGN THEM, THOUGH.

26:59.001 --> 27:01.135
OKAY, WELL, WHERE --
WHERE DO I NEED TO BE?

27:01.170 --> 27:02.970
Family court.

27:03.005 --> 27:04.972
AND WHEN WILL HE BE SERVED?

27:05.007 --> 27:06.173
TODAY.

27:06.208 --> 27:07.374
WOW, REALLY?

27:07.410 --> 27:08.609
Are you sure?

27:08.644 --> 27:09.810
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

27:09.845 --> 27:12.513
I'M GONNA MAKE THIS
REALLY EASY FOR YOU.

27:12.548 --> 27:15.516
OKAY, LISTEN, CAN WE JUST,
UM, HAVE THEM PREPARED,

27:15.551 --> 27:16.784
AND THEN I'LL GIVE YOU
A CALL BACK

27:16.819 --> 27:19.353
WHEN I FEEL IS A GOOD TIME
TO SERVE HIM?

27:19.388 --> 27:22.089
MM, WELL, NO TIME IS AS GOOD
AS THE PRESENT.

27:22.124 --> 27:23.757
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
OKAY, LISTEN, UM,

27:23.793 --> 27:25.859
THERE'S SOMEBODY AT MY DOOR,
SO I'LL --

27:25.895 --> 27:27.728
I'LL JUST CALL YOU
BACK AFTER, OKAY?

27:27.763 --> 27:29.196
-YEAH, SURE THING.
-Thanks.

27:29.231 --> 27:30.798
COME IN.

27:30.833 --> 27:33.701
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

27:33.736 --> 27:35.569
HEY.

27:35.604 --> 27:36.770
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

27:36.806 --> 27:38.772
YEAH, NO PROBLEM.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

27:38.808 --> 27:42.543
UH, I DIDN'T WANT TO TALK TO YOU
AT THE STATION.

27:42.578 --> 27:43.844
OKAY.

27:43.879 --> 27:46.513
BUT, UM, WELL, FIRST OF ALL,
I NEED TO KNOW I CAN --

27:46.549 --> 27:47.781
CAN I TRUST YOU?

27:47.817 --> 27:48.982
YEAH, OF COURSE.

27:49.018 --> 27:52.820
I'M ABOUT TO DO SOMETHING
REALLY, UM...

27:52.855 --> 27:55.122
I'M ABOUT TO DO SOMETHING THAT
COULD POTENTIALLY RUIN EDDY,

27:55.157 --> 27:59.159
AND I KNOW HE'S GONNA BE
MAD AS HELL AND...

27:59.195 --> 28:01.562
O-OKAY, WHAT IS IT?

28:01.597 --> 28:03.530
I'M GONNA TAKE CUSTODY FOR
MY DAUGHTER AWAY FROM HIM

28:03.566 --> 28:05.799
AND I'M GONNA ISSUE
A RESTRAINING ORDER.

28:05.835 --> 28:07.167
AND THAT'S A BAD THING?

28:07.203 --> 28:11.939
NO, IT'S NOT A BAD THING,
BUT HE'S NOT GONNA TAKE IT WELL.

28:11.974 --> 28:14.875
ARE YOU AFRAID OF HIM?

28:14.910 --> 28:16.110
NO.

28:16.145 --> 28:18.011
THEN WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

28:18.047 --> 28:21.448
I MEAN, I'M JUST AFRAID OF HOW
HE'S GONNA ACT AND REACT

28:21.484 --> 28:22.950
WHEN HE LOSES HIS JOB.

28:22.985 --> 28:24.785
THAT IS NOT YOUR PROBLEM.

28:24.820 --> 28:25.986
YEAH, I KNOW THAT,
STEVEN,

28:26.021 --> 28:28.789
BUT THAT JOB
IS ALL HE HAS AND --

28:28.824 --> 28:30.991
YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.
THIS GUY'S HORRIBLE.

28:31.026 --> 28:32.126
DO WE NEED TO GO
THROUGH THE LIST

28:32.161 --> 28:33.594
OF EVERYTHING THAT HE'S DONE
OVER THE YEARS?

28:33.629 --> 28:37.264
OKAY, I GET IT, BUT HE'S STILL
MY DAUGHTER'S FATHER.

28:37.299 --> 28:39.032
WELL, YOU JUST NEED TO DO
WHAT'S GOOD FOR YOU,

28:39.068 --> 28:40.200
FOR YOU
AND YOUR DAUGHTER'S SAKE.

28:40.236 --> 28:42.002
FORGET HIM.

28:42.037 --> 28:44.171
IF I DO THIS,
CAN I COUNT ON YOU?

28:44.206 --> 28:45.539
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

28:45.574 --> 28:50.010
IF I GO THROUGH WITH THIS
ALL THE WAY

28:50.045 --> 28:51.712
LIKE I INTEND TO
TO WITH EDDY,

28:51.747 --> 28:53.080
WILL YOU BE THERE
AS A FRIEND TO --

28:53.115 --> 28:56.650
TO SUPPORT ME AND HELP ME.
-YOU'RE -- YOU'RE SCARED OF HIM.

28:56.685 --> 28:58.418
NO.
NO, I'M NOT.

28:58.454 --> 29:01.722
YOU ARE.
IT'S OKAY, BUT ADMIT IT.

29:01.757 --> 29:05.125
OKAY, MAYBE --
MAYBE JUST A LITTLE.

29:05.161 --> 29:06.560
ALL RIGHT.

29:06.595 --> 29:08.662
STOP -- STOP BEING SCARED.
LET'S DO THIS.

29:08.697 --> 29:10.197
HE IS GONNA FLIP OUT.

29:10.232 --> 29:11.799
HE'S GONNA BE --

29:11.834 --> 29:13.534
WAIT, HE'S NEVER HIT YOU,
HAS HE?

29:13.569 --> 29:16.303
NO, STEVEN.
NO, I WOULD NEVER ALLOW THAT.

29:16.338 --> 29:17.838
BE HONEST WITH ME.
HAS HE EVER HIT YOU?

29:17.873 --> 29:19.940
NO, HE HASN'T.

29:19.975 --> 29:22.676
JUST WANTED TO KNOW
IF YOU HAD MY BACK, IS ALL.

29:22.711 --> 29:25.145
100%.

29:25.181 --> 29:27.848
ALL RIGHT, SO WILL YOU COME
WITH ME DOWN TO THE COURT HOUSE

29:27.883 --> 29:29.750
SO I CAN FILE
THESE PAPERS?

29:29.785 --> 29:31.084
YOU GOT THEM ALREADY?

29:31.120 --> 29:33.453
YEAH, THEY'RE BEING PROCESSED
AS WE SPEAK RIGHT NOW.

29:33.489 --> 29:34.555
WELL, LET'S GO.

29:34.590 --> 29:35.823
OKAY.
THANK YOU.

29:35.858 --> 29:37.925
-OF COURSE.
-YOU'RE SWEET.

29:37.960 --> 29:40.060
GOD, YOU'RE SHAKING,
YOU POOR THING.

29:40.095 --> 29:41.428
MM.

29:41.463 --> 29:43.030
I'VE BEEN WITH THESE KIND OF MEN
MY ENTIRE LIFE,

29:43.065 --> 29:46.099
AND IT NEVER GETS EASIER.

29:46.135 --> 29:47.367
YOU KNOW WHAT?

29:47.403 --> 29:49.169
THINGS ARE GONNA CHANGE.
OKAY?

29:49.205 --> 29:51.271
-YEAH. ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
-COOL.

29:51.307 --> 29:57.845
♪♪

29:57.880 --> 30:03.951
♪♪

30:03.986 --> 30:06.086
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

30:09.124 --> 30:11.225
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

30:12.328 --> 30:14.061
WHAT THE HELL DO YOU WANT?

30:14.096 --> 30:15.896
HEARD IT'S NOT
YOUR BABY.

30:15.931 --> 30:17.197
Get off my damn phone.

30:17.233 --> 30:18.131
NO, NO.

30:18.167 --> 30:19.766
HOW DOES IT FEEL, HUH?

30:19.802 --> 30:21.768
GUESS YOU CAN'T
MAKE A BABY, EITHER.

30:21.804 --> 30:23.170
MARCIE.

30:23.205 --> 30:25.939
HOW DOES IT FEEL, RANDAL,
TO LOSE EVERY DAMN HOPE, HMM?

30:25.975 --> 30:29.109
YOU ARE AN EVIL, EVIL BITCH.
YOU KNOW THAT?

30:29.144 --> 30:30.644
NO, NO, THAT'S YOU.

30:30.679 --> 30:32.579
YOU'RE THE EVIL ONE.
YOU'RE THE DEVIL.

30:32.615 --> 30:33.981
MARCIE, I'M NOT PLAYING.

30:34.016 --> 30:37.918
SO, WHO WAS THAT WHORE
SLEEPING WITH?

30:37.953 --> 30:40.087
-OH, YOU THINK THIS IS FUNNY?
-Yeah.

30:40.122 --> 30:43.357
YOU HAVE TO LIVE IN THAT HOUSE
RIGHT NEXT TO HER.

30:43.392 --> 30:45.792
YOU'RE AN EVIL, EVIL LI--

30:45.828 --> 30:48.095
What?
Is your heart broken, darling?

30:48.130 --> 30:49.663
WELL, SO WAS MINE.

30:49.698 --> 30:52.099
LOOKS LIKE NOW NEITHER ONE
OF US CAN HAVE ANY KIDS.

30:52.134 --> 30:53.267
OH.

30:53.302 --> 30:54.368
YOU KNOW I'M BETTER AT THIS
THAN YOU.

30:54.403 --> 30:56.036
WHAT ARE WE TALKING ABOUT,
MIND GAMES?

30:56.071 --> 30:58.972
OH, BABY.

30:59.008 --> 31:00.841
I JUST GOT STARTED.

31:00.876 --> 31:02.009
ME, TOO.

31:02.044 --> 31:03.877
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

31:03.913 --> 31:11.852
♪♪

31:11.887 --> 31:18.792
♪♪

31:18.827 --> 31:20.594
NO, NO, NO.

31:21.964 --> 31:25.098
NO, NO, NO, NO.

31:25.134 --> 31:28.468
DAMN IT!

31:28.504 --> 31:30.637
NO!

31:30.673 --> 31:32.706
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

31:36.011 --> 31:38.578
OH, YOU STUPID BITCH!

31:38.614 --> 31:41.181
WHAT THE F-- WHAT THE...

31:42.051 --> 31:44.251
OH, DAMN, MAN!

31:47.523 --> 31:49.256
OKAY.

31:49.291 --> 31:51.358
OKAY.

31:51.393 --> 31:52.526
ALL RIGHT, BITCH.

31:52.561 --> 31:55.062
ALL RIGHT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:55.097 --> 31:56.997
YOU'RE DONE.
YOU'RE DONE.

31:57.032 --> 31:58.465
YOU'RE DONE.

31:58.500 --> 32:00.934
I GOT YOU.
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:00.970 --> 32:02.235
AH -- AH, SHIT.

32:02.271 --> 32:04.404
OKAY. OKAY.

32:06.241 --> 32:07.507
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT, BITCH.

32:07.543 --> 32:09.943
YOU'RE GOOD.
YOU'RE DONE. YOU'RE DONE.

32:13.682 --> 32:15.382
Tanya:
YOU LIKE THIS, HONEY?

32:15.417 --> 32:18.986
I DO.
IT'S REALLY NICE.

32:20.889 --> 32:22.556
OKAY.
OKAY.

32:22.591 --> 32:28.495
♪♪

32:28.530 --> 32:30.230
YES, SIR, PARTNER.

32:30.265 --> 32:32.766
HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON?
WENT WELL TODAY IN COURT.

32:32.801 --> 32:34.001
YEAH?

32:34.036 --> 32:36.169
YOU WON'T BELIEVE THE DAY
THAT I'M HAVING.

32:36.205 --> 32:39.706
RANDAL FOUND OUT THAT
ALEX'S KID IS NOT HIS.

32:39.742 --> 32:41.074
RANDAL?

32:41.110 --> 32:43.477
YEAH, RANDAL HOLMES AND ALEX,
THE NEXT-DOOR NEIGHBOR.

32:43.512 --> 32:46.480
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

32:46.515 --> 32:47.948
ALEX AND RANDAL HAD A KID?

32:47.983 --> 32:49.349
MM-HMM, SO HE THOUGHT.

32:49.385 --> 32:51.518
TODAY HE FOUND OUT
THAT'S NOT THE CASE.

32:51.553 --> 32:53.120
HE'S GOING CRAZY.

32:53.155 --> 32:55.055
-WHAT?
-YEAH.

32:55.090 --> 32:56.923
SO, WHAT'D YOU WANT?

32:56.959 --> 32:58.258
OH, NOTHING, MAN.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

32:58.293 --> 32:59.893
I'LL TELL YOU LATER.
-NO, NO, NO, NO.

32:59.928 --> 33:01.895
COME ON, TELL ME NOW.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

33:01.930 --> 33:03.330
[ SIGHS ]

33:03.365 --> 33:06.166
WELL, I THINK WE GOT
A PROBLEM.

33:06.201 --> 33:07.667
WHAT ELSE IS NEW?

33:07.703 --> 33:09.703
YEAH, WELL, I THINK
SOME OF THE OFFICERS ARE ON

33:09.738 --> 33:11.538
TO ALL THE WOMEN
WE DID SETTLEMENTS FOR

33:11.573 --> 33:13.673
REGARDING THE CAINS
AND THE CHURCH.

33:13.709 --> 33:15.208
HOW THE HELL WOULD
THEY KNOW THAT?

33:15.244 --> 33:16.943
I DON'T KNOW.

33:16.979 --> 33:18.512
HAVE YOU SAID ANYTHING
TO ANYONE?

33:18.547 --> 33:19.446
NAH, MAN.

33:19.481 --> 33:20.881
NAH, I DIDN'T, MAN.
COME ON.

33:20.916 --> 33:22.416
YOU TOOK EVERYTHING I HAD,
REMEMBER?

33:22.451 --> 33:24.451
I DIDN'T SAY A WORD.

33:24.486 --> 33:26.253
SO, HOW THE HELL
DID YOU FIND OUT?

33:26.288 --> 33:29.289
WELL, YOU KNOW LUSHION'S BEEN
ASKING ME TO HELP HER.

33:29.324 --> 33:30.457
RIGHT.

33:30.492 --> 33:32.092
YEAH, HE JUST CALLED,
AND, YOU KNOW, HE ASKED ME,

33:32.127 --> 33:33.727
AND NATURALLY I SAID NO.

33:33.762 --> 33:35.662
AND HE TOLD ME
HE FOUND SOMETHING.

33:35.697 --> 33:37.764
ALL RIGHT.
GIVE ME HIS NUMBER.

33:37.800 --> 33:40.167
I GUESS I COULD DO THAT,
BUT, UH --

33:40.202 --> 33:41.435
BUT WHAT?

33:41.470 --> 33:44.171
WELL, HERE'S THE THING,
HE, UH, THINKS I'M ON HIS SIDE.

33:44.206 --> 33:46.406
I DON'T WANT TO SPOOK
HIM ON IT. I THINK WE
SHOULD PLAY THIS OUT.

33:46.442 --> 33:49.276
IAN, IF YOU'RE IN THE MIDDLE
OF ANY OF THIS, MY MAN.

33:49.311 --> 33:50.577
LISTEN, I'M NOT.

33:50.612 --> 33:52.212
PRETTY HARD TO BELIEVE
CONSIDERING YOU WERE TRYING

33:52.247 --> 33:54.147
TO HELP HER
ONTO YOUR MORAL HIGH HORSE.

33:54.183 --> 33:56.450
I'M NOT, MAN.
MY LOYALTY'S HERE.

33:56.485 --> 33:57.851
RIGHT.

33:57.886 --> 34:01.221
WELL, IAN, IF YOU'RE IN
THE MIDDLE OF ANY OF THIS,

34:01.256 --> 34:03.223
IT'S GONNA BE
A SERIOUS PROBLEM.

34:03.258 --> 34:05.559
YOU BETTER STAY ON TOP OF THIS.
OTHERWISE IT'S YOUR ASS.

34:05.594 --> 34:07.794
I'M ALL OVER IT.

34:07.830 --> 34:09.596
I KNOW.

34:09.631 --> 34:11.198
GOOD DAY, PARTNER.

34:11.233 --> 34:12.766
-I'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.
-YES, SIR.

34:15.204 --> 34:17.204
[ SIGHS ]

34:17.239 --> 34:22.008
♪♪

34:24.446 --> 34:25.679
-HEY.
-HEY.

34:25.714 --> 34:26.780
-HOW ARE YOU?
-ARE THEY HERE YET?

34:26.815 --> 34:28.281
WHO?

34:28.317 --> 34:30.250
IAN AND THAT KID LAWYER.

34:30.285 --> 34:32.285
NO. NO.

34:32.321 --> 34:34.855
LOOK, I NEED
TO TELL YOU SOMETHING.

34:34.890 --> 34:35.722
WHAT'S UP?

34:35.757 --> 34:37.657
RANDAL.

34:37.693 --> 34:39.159
HE'S BEEN STARING
AT THAT WOMAN

34:39.194 --> 34:40.760
WHO JUST MOVED IN
ACROSS THE STREET.

34:40.796 --> 34:42.062
WHAT?

34:42.097 --> 34:43.296
YEAH, HE'S BEEN LOOKING AT HER
THROUGH BINOCULARS.

34:43.332 --> 34:44.598
SOMEBODY'S GONNA KILL
THAT FOOL.

34:44.633 --> 34:46.833
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
I'LL LET YOU HANDLE THAT.

34:50.806 --> 34:53.140
HEY.
COME ON IN.

34:53.175 --> 34:55.275
-HI.
-PLEASE, HAVE A SEAT.

34:55.310 --> 35:05.185
♪♪

35:05.220 --> 35:07.521
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

35:07.556 --> 35:10.123
WE WANTED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT REPRESENTING KELLY.

35:10.159 --> 35:13.326
I THOUGHT
YOU DIDN'T WANT ME TO.

35:13.362 --> 35:16.630
I'VE CHANGED MY MIND.

35:16.665 --> 35:19.332
AND WHY DON'T YOU DO IT, IAN,
WITH YOUR REPUTATION?

35:19.368 --> 35:21.134
I CAN'T.
I GOT A CONFLICT.

35:21.170 --> 35:22.435
THIS ONE'S YOURS.

35:22.471 --> 35:24.037
YOUR REPUTATION
IS STELLAR, IAN.

35:24.072 --> 35:25.238
YES, IT IS.

35:25.274 --> 35:26.640
THAT'S WHY YOU NEED TO LISTEN
VERY CAREFULLY

35:26.675 --> 35:28.341
WHAT I'M ABOUT
TO TELL YOU.

35:28.377 --> 35:29.476
OKAY.

35:29.511 --> 35:31.578
YOU'RE GONNA WALK INTO
THE D.A.'s OFFICE,

35:31.613 --> 35:33.013
YOU'RE GONNA LAY OUT
ALL THE EVIDENCE

35:33.048 --> 35:34.681
THAT YOU HAVE
AGAINST TRAVIS CAIN,

35:34.716 --> 35:36.816
AND YOU'RE GONNA CONVINCE HER
TO DROP THE CHARGES.

35:38.754 --> 35:40.320
WHAT D.A.?

35:40.355 --> 35:41.922
HILLMORE.

35:41.957 --> 35:43.056
SHE'S TOUGH.

35:43.091 --> 35:44.891
YEAH,
BUT YOU'RE TOUGHER.

35:48.163 --> 35:50.964
-I DON'T KNOW IF I CAN DO THIS.
-NO, YOU CAN AND YOU WILL.

35:50.999 --> 35:52.265
BUT DON'T YOU THINK --

35:52.301 --> 35:53.767
LISTEN,
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

35:53.802 --> 35:55.468
WE'RE GONNA LAY OUT
EVERYTHING FOR YOU.

35:55.504 --> 35:56.736
AND I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
ALL MY NOTES, ALL RIGHT?

35:56.772 --> 35:58.805
YOU JUST GOT TO PAY
CLOSE ATTENTION TO THEM.

35:58.840 --> 36:02.976
YEAH, ALL YOU GOT TO DO
IS RELAX, BREATHE.

36:03.011 --> 36:04.277
CAN I DO THIS?

36:04.313 --> 36:06.046
YES, YOU CAN,
AND YOU WILL.

36:06.081 --> 36:07.380
I KNOW YOU CAN,
ALL RIGHT?

36:07.416 --> 36:11.318
SOMEBODY GAVE ME A SHOT.
NOW IT'S YOUR TURN.

36:11.353 --> 36:13.153
OKAY.

36:16.158 --> 36:16.990
OKAY.

36:17.025 --> 36:19.059
NOW,
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

36:19.094 --> 36:20.894
THANK YOU FOR HAVING ME.

36:23.832 --> 36:24.998
-ALL RIGHT.
-YES, SIR.

36:25.033 --> 36:26.466
REMEMBER WHAT I SAID.

36:26.501 --> 36:28.668
-GOT YOU.
-WE'LL BE IN TOUCH.

36:28.704 --> 36:30.370
ALL RIGHT.
HAVE A GOOD NIGHT.

36:30.405 --> 36:35.542
♪♪

36:35.577 --> 36:40.247
♪♪

36:40.282 --> 36:41.648
THINK HE'S
GONNA BE OKAY?

36:41.683 --> 36:43.917
